1: Verify Control Plane Health
Test Commands:

kubectl get nodes # Verify node connectivity
kubectl get pods --all-namespaces # Check pod status
kubectl cluster-info # Verify cluster information


2 Important Notes:
Check for any error messages or unusual behavior.
Verify that your applications are accessible.

3 Common Mistakes:
Proceeding to node group updates without verifying control plane stability.
Not checking the API server logs.
